# JobRoom Backend Configuration

# Security (change in production!)
SECRET_KEY=your-super-secret-random-key-here

# Gmail SMTP Configuration
# Follow these steps to get your credentials:

# 1. Enable 2-Factor Authentication on your Google Account:
#    https://myaccount.google.com/security

# 2. Create an App Password:
#    https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Select "Mail" and your device
#    - Copy the 16-character password

# 3. Fill in the values below:
SMTP_SERVER=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your.email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx
FROM_EMAIL=your.email@gmail.com

# Notes:
# - SMTP_PASS is the 16-character APP PASSWORD (not your regular Gmail password)
# - The password may have spaces - you can keep or remove them
# - FROM_EMAIL should be the same as SMTP_USER
